    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/16d9550f1236a774bffe3448805177d1.avif?t=1728716415\" width=620 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你打开梦幻的魔法书，跟着我们一起体验这万千世界！你是一位充满好奇的初学者，需要不断提高眼力，寻找世界的规律，感受时空的变换。《何处》(Where wh..?) 是一款LowPoly艺术风格的解谜找茬游戏，只是这一次，来到了三维世界，踏上寻找和探索的冒险之途，享受精美画面和悠扬音乐。很适合静下心来独自游玩，当然要是家人和朋友加入其中，这趟旅途一定更加有趣！近百个关卡，远超过10小时游戏流程，绝对量大管饱！(￣︶￣)↗ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如此美丽的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/c133b366e7e6e921501f90ad9390dbf5.poster.avif?t=1728716415\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/c133b366e7e6e921501f90ad9390dbf5.webm?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/c133b366e7e6e921501f90ad9390dbf5.mp4?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《何处》拥有完整九大主线世界内容，每个世界中场景又有完全不同的风格，涵盖各种科幻，自然，人文，历史，文化。没有单调且重复的资源堆砌，只有精致合理的设计，完美融入场景的谜题和契合氛围的背景音乐。♪(´∇`*) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典与创新并存，回归游戏本质</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/73c057ef411aa13ad90ab7e198395d22.poster.avif?t=1728716415\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/73c057ef411aa13ad90ab7e198395d22.webm?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/73c057ef411aa13ad90ab7e198395d22.mp4?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>传统找茬作品只是单纯在两幅画面中点击不同，《何处》吸取大量同类作品的优点，不是简单的缩放画面，而是通过同时改变视距和远近，带来与众不同体验，首次融入了时间和空间的概念，多种拍摄视角和转场方式，全新的创意玩法，不再是简单复制黏贴。o(￣ヘ￣o＃) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多彩的旅途</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/849a6cb5ebf30b5436541d61b2c7be88.poster.avif?t=1728716415\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/849a6cb5ebf30b5436541d61b2c7be88.webm?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/849a6cb5ebf30b5436541d61b2c7be88.mp4?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>如果只是相同的场景和重复玩法，一定会觉得不是没那么有趣。《何处》在流程中设置了不同的玩法和各种维度不同的场景，让游玩体验更加丰富多彩，加上流畅的游玩体验，完整的收集道具和各种隐藏在场景中的成就。相信我！静下心投入其中，一定能找到很多乐趣！(。・∀・)ノ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全面的个性化设置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/ed728c78830998f81d13ba54f07fb60a.poster.avif?t=1728716415\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/ed728c78830998f81d13ba54f07fb60a.webm?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/ed728c78830998f81d13ba54f07fb60a.mp4?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>我们在设置中加入了很多个性化选项，为了玩起来有趣又舒心，随时可以打开设置中调整。偷偷告诉你，打开窗口模式，可以进一步提高游戏体验，2：1的宽屏画面，让视野足够开阔，让人身临其境！ヽ(￣ω￣(￣ω￣〃)ゝ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战眼力的边界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/dff6c94144d5beaf90ea47a698d79ce0.poster.avif?t=1728716415\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/dff6c94144d5beaf90ea47a698d79ce0.webm?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277380/extras/dff6c94144d5beaf90ea47a698d79ce0.mp4?t=1728716415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>任何想深入体验解谜找茬乐趣的玩家，都可以在《何处》中得到真正的满足。“回响模式”作为游戏中期解锁的高难度设计，去掉所有提示，全新的收集资源，全面翻新的场景，挑战你的所有视觉神经！(￣△￣；) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于我们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《何处》是PitaGame上线的第二款作品，我们是来自上海的两人独立工作室，致力于制作相同类型下具有独一无二气质的作品。游戏嘛（´v｀），很多时候只有试过才知道，随后会上线Demo，希望大家喜欢~ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想获取更多更有趣的游戏~ 关注我们！第三款作品也会尽快到来~</p>",
